Package: tg.blockr
Title: Interactive Blocks for Canton Thurgau Data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    c(person("Christoph", "Sax", , "christoph@cynkra.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7192-7044")),
      person("Layal Christine", "Lettry", , "layal@cynkra.com", role = "aut",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0008-6396-0523")))
Description: Extends 'blockr.core' with interactive blocks for working with
    Canton Thurgau datasets. Provides a visual interface to load and explore
    datasets from the 'tg.data' package without writing code. The TG Data block
    allows users to select from all available Thurgau datasets, choose between
    loading from the data lake (faster) or directly from the internet, configure
    label addition, and run validation through a graphical interface.
